parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.What the hell do you ladies think you’re doing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeBaEx.It’s not who you think it is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoOp^.They left you here? Is the rift really closed?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArMaAg^.You are a lying demon! Erica’s soul is surely in the Empyrean.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnEx^.She’s not going to hang around Limbo. Souls don’t linger there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.She was not supposed to look at the Toma.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Then why did you give it to Kimberly to show everyone?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnEx^.You should have thought about that before you put the Toma back together.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnDe^.She won’t go to Hell. What are you talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.This body… It can be given back to Erica, but it must be on my turf.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.You mean… Her soul can go back into her body?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.The rift will allow this body to enter Hell… I can give it to her, but I need Madalyn’s body back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnDe.Would you rather I keep Erica’s body?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How do we make Erica go to Hell?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoOp^.How does Erica commit blasphemy if she’s already dead?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.She must use a holy relic as a sex toy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArShClNo1^.That’s a sin against God! An unforgivable sin!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnDe^.You would damn her to Hell just to bring her back to Earth? I will not be a part of this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.The angel must do it. She has access to Limbo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.I’m probably Hell-bound. Could you kill me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEDe.You would never find her. Limbo is many times bigger than your world…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Arianna… Erica isn’t supposed to be dead… How is that God’s will?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiSaOp.This is my fault… I should have been more careful.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.This is not your fault! The only one to blame is the fucking God who set this into motion!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArAnEx^.I will help… But I will not tell Erica to sin against God.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.Erica deserves to live. Tell her what to do and I’ll save her when she enters Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArBaDe^.I will try… But I will not risk falling from grace… I do not want to become a demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.Now give me back my body and Erica’s will be yours to hold safe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnOp^.Any funny business and I’ll cut your head off.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiAnEx.Don’t let the angel fail us… Don’t let her value herself over Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlDe.Too bad. You could have had a lot of fun.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoEx^.My phone is linked to my Lustagram account!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx.She’s going to post the Toma to Lustagram.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Shit! We’re running out of time. We need to find the amulets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeWoEx.We better not piss off the demon if we expect her to save Erica’s soul.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We’ll find a holy relic and the amulets… Let’s work fast.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoOp^.There must be something to wear around here.");
